      <h2>A Legacy Built on <em>Trust &amp; Integrity</em></h2>

      <p class="story-lead">Nusrat International was founded with a singular vision — to provide Bangladeshi families with safe, legal, and dignified pathways to opportunity abroad.</p>

      <p>What began as a humble travel agency in the commercial heart of Banani, Dhaka has grown into one of Bangladesh's most recognized names in two critical sectors: international manpower recruitment and travel services. Under the steady leadership of <strong>Alhaj Mohammad Zakir Hossain</strong>, the company has maintained an unwavering commitment to ethical practice, regulatory compliance, and genuine care for every client.</p>

      <p>Today, Nusrat International operates two distinct but complementary divisions — <strong>Nusrat International</strong> for manpower recruiting and <strong>Nusrat Travels</strong> for aviation and tour services — both operating from the same Banani address and guided by the same values that have defined the organization from day one.</p>

      <p>Our membership in BAIRA and ATAB, combined with IATA accreditation, reflects not just credentials on paper, but a lived commitment to operating with transparency, dignity, and care for every person who walks through our door.</p>

      <div class="story-quote">
        <blockquote>"Our mission has always been simple: to serve our clients as if they were our own family — with honesty, care, and full accountability."</blockquote>
        <cite>— Alhaj Mohammad Zakir Hossain, Proprietor</cite>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

